window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>All stories come to an end, and thankfully this one is very cozy.</p> <p>In the final installment of Dark Lord of the Farmstead, find out what becomes of the Stillwater family. Mild spoilers: it's wholesome.</p> <p>As Gray continues to take care of his family every way he can, while also juggling politics every now and then, Narya is planning a birthday surprise for her husband. Kaya is still coming to grips with what she's become, but Meeko has a plan--and a quest--to help her. It involves some monsters, some fishing, and a healthy dose of adventure.</p> <p>Level up in this final installment of Dark Lord of the Farmstead. Try not to get too sniffly!</p>"; 
